{"id":464,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":66,"title":"66. I'll Take You","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":11,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you.464/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you-2022-03-07-21-26-45/0-66-ill-take-you.mp3","transcript":"Diana!\nOh, George... hi, how are you?\nListen, I'm in a terrible hurry.\nThe bank closes in twenty minutes.\nIs your bank near here?\nYes, it's only four blocks away, on Vine Street.\nWell, get in. I'll take you.\nAre you sure? It's not out of your way?\nNo, not at all.\nThat is so nice of you, George. Thank you.\nYou're welcome.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:56","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Diana!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you-2022-03-07-21-26-45/1.mp3","time_start":2.35,"time_end":3.26},{"position":2,"content":"Oh, George... hi, how are you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you-2022-03-07-21-26-45/2.mp3","time_start":3.26,"time_end":5.65},{"position":3,"content":"Listen, I'm in a terrible hurry.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you-2022-03-07-21-26-45/3.mp3","time_start":5.65,"time_end":7.69},{"position":4,"content":"The bank closes in twenty minutes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you-2022-03-07-21-26-45/4.mp3","time_start":7.69,"time_end":9.64},{"position":5,"content":"Is your bank near here?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you-2022-03-07-21-26-45/5.mp3","time_start":9.65,"time_end":10.8},{"position":6,"content":"Yes, it's only four blocks away, on Vine Street.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/66-ill-take-you-2022-03-07-21-26-45/6.mp3"